Not burning,<break time="1.5s"/> but <emphasis level="moderate">soothing</emphasis>.<break time="2s"/> Like sunlight after rain.<break time="4s"/>

And the Physician whispers:<break time="3s"/>

"You were never broken.<break time="2.5s"/> You were only learning to protect yourself.<break time="3s"/> But here,<break time="1.5s"/> you are safe to <emphasis level="moderate">open</emphasis> again."<break time="5s"/>

