You take it,<break time="2s"/> and as you do,<break time="2s"/> you feel its warmth spreading through your entire body.<break time="4s"/>

This is the fire of renewal.<break time="2.5s"/> The proof that you can rise.<break time="3s"/> That love is not lost,<break time="2s"/> only <emphasis level="moderate">transformed</emphasis>.<break time="5s"/>

